title: I heard Fiora got picked in a pro game in some region?
body:
Can anyone give me the link to that game I don't believe it lol.
I think someone said it was in the LMS Taiwan

replies.body:
LMS has a Galio, Morde, Wukong and Master Yi.

BR (CBLoL) has a Katarina.

But I haven't heard of a Fiora in a competitive play this season.
look up Fiora LMS Taiwan on youtube and check for yourself. I have no idea, but it's worth a look.
